query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(ci n mk) NoHashJoin(ci mk n t) NoMergeJoin(ci mk n t k) */ select min(k.keyword) AS movie_keyword,
min(n.name) AS actor_name,
min(t.title) AS hero_movie
from name AS n
inner join cast_info AS ci
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.name like '%Smith,%'
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1998
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('superhero',
'blood',
'based-on-comic',
'fight',
'tv-special',
'web',
'superhero',
'fight');
